<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Spyderbot</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f0f;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      background: #111;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .btn {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: #00ff88;
      color: black;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Spyderbot</h1>
  <p>Robot inteligente de riego automatizado</p>
  <button class="btn">Contacto: uvspyderbot</button>
</header>

<section>
  <h2>Proyecto</h2>
  <p>Este sistema automatiza el riego de plantas usando robótica móvil tipo teleférico.</p>
</section>

<footer>
  © 2026 Spyderbot
</footer>

</body>
</html>